  <li id="comment-2749" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="http://beccaandbella.blogspot.com/" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Becca</a></cite></div>
      <a href="index.html?p=1690#comment-2749"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2006-01-14T03:57:00-05:00">Saturday, January 14, 2006 at 3:57 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
